column5: Got back from my Alaska trip this evening and thought I would tease y'all with a few pics. These were taken with my little Olympus p&s camera. Lots to come including tons on my good camera later. Sleep first.
Very nice !!!! Awesome scenery up there !!!!
I was wondern wherez ya were at.  This is a super cool shot. That could go on the back window of my truck.     Cant wait to see the rest.
nice looking forward to the report
Found these samsquench prints while I was there.

Looking forward to the full report!        This is a super cool shot. That could go on the back window of my truck.     Cant wait to see the rest.  You should wrap your entire truck and put a flaming turkey on the hood. That would be cool.
I agree , that mountain shot is amazing . Love the reports from the north , can't wait !
Looking good Dave,can't wait for the rest.You must of had or heard a few good stories ??.
Looking forward to the full report!       You should wrap your entire truck and put a flaming turkey on the hood. That would be cool.
Sweet, can't wait or the rest!

Hey Dave It's been many years since you invited me to share your  hallowed ground. I remember it like it was yesterday! Your photos just enrich those memories! I must content myself with eastern GL fish for another year, but hope to head west next year. Thanks for giving us the teaser!
Great shots.......can't wait for the full report.
